<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٢١٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6401">‌مُوسَى بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ، </a>نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1130">‌جَرِيرٌ، </a>نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1663">‌حُمَيْدٌ -<span class="c5"> يَعْنِي:</span> ابْنَ هِلَالٍ - </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2316">‌سَعْدِ بْنِ هِشَامِ بْنِ عَامِرٍ، </a>بِهَذَا الْحَدِيثِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>